  "text": "The associate editor coordinating the review of this manuscript and approving it for publication was Andrei Muller. some theories and experiments have shown that electrons transfer from the C-H diamond: hydrogen side to the surface adsorbates after the hydrogenation treatment on the surface of diamond [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . Therefore, a two-dimensional hole gas layer (2DHG) is formed near the diamond surface [CITATION_3] . As a result, a similar modeling method to AlGaN/GaN HEMTs can be expanded to the diamond FETs. Due to the fast development of diamond FETs, it is time to develop a compact large-signal model for the perspective microwave circuits.",
